{"tid":1722235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"USCC稱若解放軍介入應撤銷香港特殊地位","createTime":"2019-11-15T00:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:11:54.000Z","uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5dade597da080a1ebd4d781893d26ff133f6f1","tid":1722235,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:16:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國國會一個委員會發表報告，指若中方出動解放軍軍事介入香港局勢，就應該中止香港特殊地位。<br />\n<br />\n這份年度報告由美中經濟及安全檢討委員會發表，指北京正尋求建立世界級軍隊，亦意圖以軍事行動捍衛利益，華府嘗試爭取最好狀況的同時亦必須為最壞情況做打算。<br />\n<br />\n一旦解放軍強行軍事介入香港，美方應立法中止本港特殊關稅地位，國會亦指示國務院設立指標評估香港「高度自治」情況。<br />\n<br />\n台灣方面，報告促請國防部研究為期15年的行動計劃，阻止北京武統台灣，並立法令華府增加對台軍事交流與訓練。<br />\n<br />\n報告並無約束力，中國駐華盛頓大使館未有回應。"},{"pid":"a024fba84397e03c25086089f9ee96be979f8b1c","tid":1722235,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c151b1a47f29bae672553bda41ac7f6c554d8857","tid":1722235,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e9ff1be4020397144f40631102c97a66d4f74b","tid":1722235,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69e0e6bbcc6df61750894adbc987fd2e4d1fcb3","tid":1722235,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8afab502f59a957c2f910a4c2575e431eafa41","tid":1722235,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f69e0e6bbcc6df61750894adbc987fd2e4d1fcb3","tid":1722235,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/face